From b38298f200b64599ad79d73b3ae619ff73ecb25a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: fi3 <email@email.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 08:10:18 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 3/4] ADD Vim-style terminal visual selection so focused pane
 text can be copied

Let command-mode users select text from the focused terminal pane with character, line, and block visual modes and yank it through OSC52. Keep the selection state inside the terminal UI so controller and provider workflows remain unchanged, and cover both the UI harness and terminal app paths.
